<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <img src="/images/BluCollar-Logo.jpeg" alt="Logo" />
    <p>
      Awesome job <%= @employee.profile.name %>!
      Your application has been successfully delivered to <%= @job.company %>. Look forward to them contacting you soon about the <%= @job.title %>. 
    </p><p>
      <% if @jobs.length > 1 %>
      Make sure to check out these other jobs that you matched with.
      <% elsif @jobs.length = 1 %>
      Make sure to check out this other job that you matched with.
      <% end %>
    </p>
    <% @jobs.each do |job| %>
        <h3><%= job.title %></h3>
        <h4><%= job.employer.name %></h4>
        <p><%= job.address %></p>
        <p><%= job.description %></p>
    <% end %>
    <p>
      To login to the site, just follow this link: <%= @url %>.
    </p>
    <p>Happy job-hunting and have a great day!</p>
    <p>BluCollar</p>
  </body>
</html>